                                    "description": "TestFlight quota is only available to [sponsors](https://github.com/sponsors/nekohasekai) (one-time sponsorships are accepted). Once you donate, you can get an invitation by join our Telegram group for sponsors from [@yet_another_sponsor_bot](https://t.me/yet_another_sponsor_bot) or sending us your Apple ID [via email](mailto:contact@sagernet.org)."
                                }
                            ]
                        },
